  "description": "Terran said something that prompted me to imagine what Ska \u0026ldquo;theme song\u0026rdquo; would be\u0026hellip; and then I realized I\u0026rsquo;m not sure where/how to put Terran and Ska, in my files. Making emsenn.net not be bleedy-as-heck, with links, is gonna be tough!\nPart of why I\u0026rsquo;ve compartmentalized things into subdirectories is to make it easier to keep some things private, but this ultimately means I have to think about how much I\u0026rsquo;m leaking. I guess I\u0026rsquo;m stuck between a few different places. Let me think about it\u0026hellip;\n",
